		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;564&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1354px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;mkdir -p elysia/elysia1/elysia2  多层创建目录&lt;/p&gt;
