&lt;p&gt;ls -lh elysia（ll -h elysia） 让文件大小变为人类可读形式&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://Elysia492.github.io/p/elysia03/index.assets/image-20260318192629909.png&#34;
	width=&#34;636&#34;
	height=&#34;172&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://Elysia492.github.io/p/elysia03/index.assets/image-20260318192629909_hu4240638974906176631.png 480w, https://Elysia492.github.io/p/elysia03/index.assets/image-20260318192629909_hu9181234818166386260.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;image-20260318192629909&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
